WEBVTT

00:00:02.377 --> 00:00:04.754
WRITTEN BY HYUGA NATSU

00:01:32.050 --> 00:01:32.883
{\an8}THIS STORY IS A FICTION AND ALL NAMES OF
FIGURES AND ORGANIZATIONS ARE FICTITIOUS.

00:01:32.884 --> 00:01:35.929
{\an8}I never intended to let you meet Mother.

00:01:37.013 --> 00:01:39.891
I had to pretend
you were "a new apothecary."

00:01:40.975 --> 00:01:45.396
Father says she was not like this
in the past, but,

00:01:46.397 --> 00:01:47.899
who knows.

00:01:48.566 --> 00:01:51.945
To me, she has always been
that kind of woman, ever since I was born.

00:01:52.529 --> 00:01:56.115
<i>She bullied my sister,
mistreated young maids,</i>

00:01:56.116 --> 00:01:58.451
<i>corrupted our female relatives.</i>

00:01:59.410 --> 00:02:01.620
Father never says a word.

00:02:01.621 --> 00:02:04.164
No, he cannot. He cannot go against her.

00:02:04.165 --> 00:02:07.752
He just keeps waiting for her forgiveness.

00:02:09.504 --> 00:02:12.673
Once she has a child,
she devours the husband.

00:02:12.674 --> 00:02:14.341
Like an insect.

00:02:14.342 --> 00:02:16.886
No, insects are better,

00:02:17.929 --> 00:02:20.765
they do it to ensure
their offspring survive.

00:02:22.225 --> 00:02:25.103
I do not want to become like her.

00:02:25.937 --> 00:02:29.064
<i>Shisui had even taken
abortifacients herself.</i>

00:02:29.065 --> 00:02:31.108
<i>She refused to become a mother.</i>

00:02:31.109 --> 00:02:34.444
<i>To her, there is only one "mother."</i>

00:02:34.445 --> 00:02:37.614
<i>But she never wanted to
become like Shenmei.</i>

00:02:37.615 --> 00:02:39.367
<i>That must be the real reason.</i>

00:02:40.034 --> 00:02:43.829
I looked into you a little, Maomao.

00:02:43.830 --> 00:02:47.708
Your father is a senior official, and you
were raised by a former court physician.

00:02:47.709 --> 00:02:49.918
You remind me of Sister.

00:02:49.919 --> 00:02:52.421
I do not have a father or a mother.

00:02:52.422 --> 00:02:54.007
Only an old man.

00:02:54.966 --> 00:02:57.135
Sister used to say
something like that too.

00:02:58.136 --> 00:03:00.804
Yes. I suppose so.

00:03:00.805 --> 00:03:04.017
She probably was never my sister at all.

00:03:05.435 --> 00:03:07.644
Father is a <i>tanuki.</i>

00:03:07.645 --> 00:03:10.814
Maybe he was plotting something by keeping
Sister, who carries imperial blood,

00:03:10.815 --> 00:03:12.400
close to him.

00:03:13.776 --> 00:03:14.777
So,

00:03:15.445 --> 00:03:18.740
Sister has nothing to do with
the Shi clan.

00:03:19.324 --> 00:03:20.575
<i>Liar.</i>

00:03:21.659 --> 00:03:24.037
<i>The way she looked just now,
they really are alike.</i>

00:03:24.621 --> 00:03:28.040
<i>Shisui adores her sister Suirei.</i>

00:03:28.041 --> 00:03:32.378
<i>That's why, even in this situation,
she's defending her as irrelevant.</i>

00:03:33.212 --> 00:03:35.881
<i>But that logic will not hold.</i>

00:03:35.882 --> 00:03:39.427
<i>Suirei has been far too involved
in all these incidents.</i>

00:03:45.642 --> 00:03:47.227
Hey, Maomao.

00:03:48.853 --> 00:03:51.521
If these children were insects,

00:03:51.522 --> 00:03:53.398
they might have survived the winter.

00:03:53.399 --> 00:03:55.360
<i>If they were insects?</i>

00:03:56.236 --> 00:03:58.445
Insects cannot survive winter.

00:03:58.446 --> 00:04:00.573
They just leave behind their young.

00:04:02.033 --> 00:04:03.825
<i>So that is it.</i>

00:04:03.826 --> 00:04:06.746
<i>That is why she brought me here.</i>

00:04:07.330 --> 00:04:08.665
<i>Shisui.</i>

00:04:09.582 --> 00:04:10.667
<i>Shisui is</i>

00:04:11.501 --> 00:04:13.169
<i>not coming back.</i>

00:04:16.005 --> 00:04:17.173
Shisui.

00:04:20.510 --> 00:04:22.345
<i>She should have run.</i>

00:04:23.263 --> 00:04:24.930
<i>Thrown it all away</i>

00:04:24.931 --> 00:04:27.725
<i>and escaped with Suirei.</i>

00:04:28.393 --> 00:04:32.104
<i>Throw away politics, parents, the clan,</i>

00:04:32.105 --> 00:04:33.898
<i>everything.</i>

00:04:35.275 --> 00:04:37.943
<i>Even I do not care about other people</i>

00:04:37.944 --> 00:04:39.946
<i>I only care about myself.</i>

00:04:40.697 --> 00:04:44.367
<i>Do you have any idea what I have
been through since being brought here?</i>

00:04:45.827 --> 00:04:46.869
<i>And yet.</i>

00:04:54.127 --> 00:04:55.169
<i>Why?</i>

00:04:56.045 --> 00:04:58.548
<i>Why can I never stop myself
from reaching out?</i>

00:05:01.384 --> 00:05:02.135
Do not stop me.

00:05:04.345 --> 00:05:05.763
I have

00:05:06.347 --> 00:05:08.056
a duty of my own.

00:05:08.057 --> 00:05:09.517
Does it even mean anything?

00:05:10.518 --> 00:05:12.477
It is pride. My pride.

00:05:12.478 --> 00:05:15.231
Then throw it away.

00:05:19.986 --> 00:05:21.820
Hey, Maomao.

00:05:21.821 --> 00:05:25.449
If you had a chance
to drink an unknown poison,

00:05:25.450 --> 00:05:29.077
just once, what would you do?

00:05:29.078 --> 00:05:30.913
I would drink it.

00:05:31.581 --> 00:05:32.540
Thought so.

00:05:36.377 --> 00:05:38.796
<i>She is leaving.</i>

00:05:39.714 --> 00:05:41.798
<i>But I do not know what to say</i>

00:05:41.799 --> 00:05:43.217
<i>to stop her!</i>

00:05:46.763 --> 00:05:47.805
Shisui!

00:05:48.723 --> 00:05:51.893
At least let me make a wish.

00:05:54.062 --> 00:05:55.396
A wish?

00:05:56.773 --> 00:05:58.440
That is not like you.

00:05:58.441 --> 00:06:01.652
Just this once, okay? Just once.

00:06:03.237 --> 00:06:06.281
I want it back someday. It's a gift.

00:06:06.282 --> 00:06:09.284
Do not ask the impossible.
I might just sell it off.

00:06:09.285 --> 00:06:11.788
That is fine by me.

00:06:16.334 --> 00:06:18.877
The collar, not the hair?

00:06:18.878 --> 00:06:21.798
{\an8}If you put anything more in your hair,
it will be too flashy.

00:06:24.425 --> 00:06:27.136
Your face and hair are
already covered in soot.

00:06:29.055 --> 00:06:31.933
You are right, I look like a <i>tanuki.</i>

00:06:32.725 --> 00:06:34.811
Thank you, Maomao.

00:06:43.986 --> 00:06:45.655
I leave the rest to you.

00:06:54.455 --> 00:06:57.041
"I leave the rest to you," huh.

00:07:05.174 --> 00:07:08.302
{\an8}<i>Let us go back a little in time.</i>

00:07:10.721 --> 00:07:13.056
Time is of the essence!

00:07:13.057 --> 00:07:15.809
Had our departure been delayed any longer,

00:07:15.810 --> 00:07:18.186
I might have dragged you here by force!

00:07:18.187 --> 00:07:20.439
Father, if one were to raise a hand

00:07:20.440 --> 00:07:22.524
against royalty,

00:07:22.525 --> 00:07:25.528
would only that person
be held accountable?

00:07:26.654 --> 00:07:30.116
- Lahan.
- Yes?

00:07:30.700 --> 00:07:35.455
Did you realize it?
That Jinshi and I are the same person.

00:07:35.955 --> 00:07:40.709
Yes. Height, weight, chest, waist.

00:07:40.710 --> 00:07:44.297
It is rare for all those numbers
to match exactly.

00:07:44.881 --> 00:07:48.885
Such beauty.
It is a pity you are not a woman.

00:07:49.719 --> 00:07:53.264
{\an8}Now then, let us go over the strategy
for taking the fortress.

00:07:54.348 --> 00:07:56.850
This region is rich in forest resources

00:07:56.851 --> 00:08:00.146
and has long been protected
by the Shi clan.

00:08:00.730 --> 00:08:05.860
Our investigation shows iron goods
are being routed to Shishou.

00:08:06.360 --> 00:08:10.030
On top of that,
there are hot springs in the area,

00:08:10.031 --> 00:08:11.616
so sulfur is easy to obtain.

00:08:12.742 --> 00:08:15.870
There also appear to be caves
from which saltpetre can be extracted.

00:08:16.454 --> 00:08:21.166
Sulfur and saltpetre... Combine those
and you have gunpowder.

00:08:21.167 --> 00:08:23.585
Shishou is likely stockpiling firearms

00:08:23.586 --> 00:08:25.588
in preparation for battle.

00:08:26.172 --> 00:08:29.841
- Feifa?
- Those are ill-suited to siege warfare.

00:08:29.842 --> 00:08:33.471
If you want to wipe out enemies
from atop the walls.

00:08:34.597 --> 00:08:35.598
Cannons, then.

00:08:38.768 --> 00:08:43.188
We will likely suffer major losses
just approaching the fortress.

00:08:43.189 --> 00:08:44.856
How troublesome.

00:08:44.857 --> 00:08:50.111
However, it is theoretically possible to
suppress them without allowing cannon use.

00:08:50.112 --> 00:08:52.322
Even this walking abacus agrees.

00:08:52.323 --> 00:08:53.783
So what is the plan?

00:08:54.367 --> 00:08:56.284
We strike the gunpowder store first,

00:08:56.285 --> 00:08:58.538
before they can use the cannons.

00:08:59.288 --> 00:09:02.166
It is a bit of an unorthodox tactic.

00:09:04.001 --> 00:09:04.835
I see.

00:09:05.586 --> 00:09:07.754
It would be highly cost-effective.

00:09:07.755 --> 00:09:08.798
However,

00:09:09.298 --> 00:09:10.715
there is an issue.

00:09:10.716 --> 00:09:12.385
What issue?

00:09:13.302 --> 00:09:16.180
A surprise attack... by the Forbidden Army?

00:09:17.014 --> 00:09:17.974
<i>The Forbidden Army,</i>

00:09:18.558 --> 00:09:20.600
<i>the army directly under the Emperor.</i>

00:09:20.601 --> 00:09:24.855
<i>That means we must
carry out this operation with dignity.</i>

00:09:28.985 --> 00:09:30.528
{\an8}I agree with the Grand Commandant,

00:09:31.279 --> 00:09:32.947
we must minimize casualties.

00:09:33.864 --> 00:09:34.824
Understood.

00:09:35.491 --> 00:09:37.326
- Then, Lahan.
- Yes.

00:09:39.662 --> 00:09:44.041
From now on, you will need to change
how you deal with that girl.

00:09:44.917 --> 00:09:46.127
{\an8}I am aware.

00:09:48.838 --> 00:09:51.799
Lord Lakan.
A report from the scouting unit.

00:09:52.758 --> 00:09:54.593
The snow is expected to stop by nightfall.

00:09:54.594 --> 00:09:56.761
The operation can proceed.

00:09:56.762 --> 00:09:59.139
Have the Fire Squad move out immediately.

00:09:59.140 --> 00:10:00.558
Yes, sir!

00:10:01.851 --> 00:10:03.935
Wait for me, Maomao.

00:10:03.936 --> 00:10:06.897
Papa's coming to save you.

00:10:11.694 --> 00:10:13.404
<i>I cannot sleep.</i>

00:10:14.030 --> 00:10:17.742
<i>There is still time
before the Forbidden Army arrives.</i>

00:10:19.827 --> 00:10:23.748
<i>They are deliberately indulging in
pleasure in a place where I can hear you.</i>

00:10:24.749 --> 00:10:27.292
<i>She has gathered only those women
from the clan</i>

00:10:27.293 --> 00:10:30.462
<i>who bore children and were seen
as virtuous wives and mothers,</i>

00:10:30.463 --> 00:10:33.716
<i>just to watch them degrade themselves
with male courtesans.</i>

00:10:35.843 --> 00:10:38.679
<i>She was not that kind of woman.</i>

00:10:46.771 --> 00:10:49.481
Oh, the Forbidden army has not moved yet.

00:10:49.482 --> 00:10:51.942
That shock just now.

00:10:53.653 --> 00:10:54.654
Oh!

00:10:55.696 --> 00:10:58.449
The underground gunpowder workshop?

00:10:59.158 --> 00:11:00.701
I must act fast.

00:11:03.454 --> 00:11:06.331
<i>Even though I know that, I cannot move.</i>

00:11:06.332 --> 00:11:08.167
<i>How pathetic.</i>

00:11:09.293 --> 00:11:12.254
<i>I have not had a proper night's sleep
in 20 years.</i>

00:11:13.339 --> 00:11:16.550
<i>That was when my suffering began.</i>

00:11:17.510 --> 00:11:19.220
I have a favor to ask of you.

00:11:20.346 --> 00:11:24.475
I want you to take my daughter
as your wife.

00:11:25.184 --> 00:11:29.187
She was cast out of the Imperial Court
as the daughter of a court physician

00:11:29.188 --> 00:11:31.606
who had an illicit affair with Taihou,

00:11:31.607 --> 00:11:34.360
and she has suffered greatly since.

00:11:35.194 --> 00:11:37.195
She should have lived
in the Imperial Court

00:11:37.196 --> 00:11:40.783
as a proper Imperial princess,
lacking for nothing.

00:11:41.951 --> 00:11:44.245
<i>I had no desire to marry,</i>

00:11:44.954 --> 00:11:49.750
<i>but I couldn't refuse the former
emperor's plea as he grew weaker daily.</i>

00:11:50.334 --> 00:11:54.088
Shishou, you are my loyal retainer.

00:11:54.964 --> 00:11:59.343
If you accept,
I will grant you anything you desire.

00:12:00.886 --> 00:12:05.182
<i>I had a fiancée,
who had entered the rear palace.</i>

00:12:07.518 --> 00:12:10.061
If you truly will grant me anything.

00:12:10.062 --> 00:12:15.525
<i>I took the former emperor's daughter
as my wife, and Suirei was born.</i>

00:12:15.526 --> 00:12:20.488
<i>Then my fiancée, Shenmei,
came back from the rear palace,</i>

00:12:20.489 --> 00:12:22.741
<i>and this is the result.</i>

00:12:32.585 --> 00:12:34.419
What was that noise just now?

00:12:34.420 --> 00:12:37.047
I am just about to find out.

00:12:40.759 --> 00:12:44.012
What are you wearing, Loulan?
Such indecency.

00:12:44.013 --> 00:12:46.931
I would rather not hear that from you.

00:12:46.932 --> 00:12:50.101
You abandon your children
and indulge in pleasure.

00:12:50.102 --> 00:12:52.354
You have no right to speak.

00:12:58.194 --> 00:12:59.360
Loulan?

00:12:59.361 --> 00:13:02.822
<i>Is this, really my daughter?</i>

00:13:02.823 --> 00:13:05.825
<i>I always thought she was
obedient to Shenmei, like a doll,</i>

00:13:05.826 --> 00:13:08.537
<i>dressing up however she was told.</i>

00:13:10.414 --> 00:13:13.083
Sister, I am sorry I am late.

00:13:15.461 --> 00:13:18.172
<i>She is far too practiced for this
to be her first time.</i>

00:13:18.839 --> 00:13:22.843
<i>I knew Shenmei resented Suirei,</i>

00:13:23.552 --> 00:13:26.597
<i>but to think she was beaten
like this regularly</i>

00:13:27.306 --> 00:13:30.559
<i>while I was away at Imperial Court.</i>

00:13:31.268 --> 00:13:34.104
<i>What a failure of a father I am.</i>

00:13:35.606 --> 00:13:36.815
Father.

00:13:38.484 --> 00:13:41.737
Take responsibility, at least at the end.

00:13:43.364 --> 00:13:44.198
Loulan.

00:13:45.324 --> 00:13:48.410
You are the old <i>tanuki</i> of Fox Village.

00:13:49.328 --> 00:13:51.747
Let us keep up the illusion
to the very end.

00:14:07.221 --> 00:14:08.681
What! What is this?

00:14:20.109 --> 00:14:21.277
An avalanche?

00:14:21.861 --> 00:14:25.029
The armory!
If that gets buried, we cannot fight!

00:14:25.030 --> 00:14:27.991
There is no gunpowder either. I burned it.

00:14:27.992 --> 00:14:29.868
Loulan, you!

00:14:29.869 --> 00:14:32.204
You knew we could not win this fight.

00:14:32.872 --> 00:14:36.709
Father, I will stay with Mother.

00:14:38.878 --> 00:14:41.338
Take responsibility, huh?

00:14:43.340 --> 00:14:44.341
Yes.

00:14:45.467 --> 00:14:47.219
This is my responsibility.

00:14:48.304 --> 00:14:50.221
The armory's been buried in snow!

00:14:50.222 --> 00:14:51.557
Get more men!

00:14:52.141 --> 00:14:54.351
There's no time
before the Forbidden Army attacks.

00:14:58.022 --> 00:15:01.317
Whoa! Enemy assault!

00:15:06.030 --> 00:15:08.072
Forbidden Army? When did they get here?

00:15:08.073 --> 00:15:09.408
Fight back!

00:15:18.250 --> 00:15:21.629
The enemy is in chaos! Strike all at once!

00:15:27.509 --> 00:15:31.055
Do not kill those who have
no will to fight. Capture them!

00:15:32.264 --> 00:15:34.307
Fewer soldiers than I expected.

00:15:34.308 --> 00:15:36.351
It seems many of the frontline troops

00:15:36.352 --> 00:15:39.979
moved toward the buildings
to deal with the fire.

00:15:39.980 --> 00:15:41.815
- We move forward.
- Yes, sir!

00:15:42.441 --> 00:15:45.319
I can't believe such a reckless plan
actually worked.

00:15:46.779 --> 00:15:50.073
But even more surprising
is that the old man Shishou,

00:15:50.074 --> 00:15:52.367
who they used to call
a wily old <i>tanuki</i> in court,

00:15:52.368 --> 00:15:54.578
is holed up in a place like this.

00:15:55.454 --> 00:15:56.455
<i>But more than that,</i>

00:15:57.289 --> 00:16:00.792
<i>the real shock was the so-called
heavenly maiden of a eunuch,</i>

00:16:00.793 --> 00:16:04.212
<i>who turned out to be the commander</i>

00:16:04.213 --> 00:16:06.507
<i>of the Forbidden Army.</i>

00:16:07.091 --> 00:16:10.593
Some might say this plan does not suit

00:16:10.594 --> 00:16:13.554
a royal commanding the Forbidden Army.

00:16:13.555 --> 00:16:16.641
But if we want to minimize our casualties,

00:16:16.642 --> 00:16:18.519
it was the best course of action.

00:16:19.436 --> 00:16:21.688
I made that judgment myself.

00:16:21.689 --> 00:16:25.109
I will take the blame
for the false strategy!

00:16:25.985 --> 00:16:28.487
<i>Seriously, what kind of head comes up
with a plan like this,</i>

00:16:29.154 --> 00:16:31.322
<i>and what kind of person</i>

00:16:31.323 --> 00:16:32.950
<i>actually follows through with it?</i>

00:16:35.911 --> 00:16:38.955
Hey, you! What is the situation inside?

00:16:38.956 --> 00:16:43.210
We need to put out the fire quickly,
or Madame will.

00:16:46.255 --> 00:16:47.381
Wait!

00:16:48.841 --> 00:16:51.092
- Any advice?
- Yes.

00:16:51.093 --> 00:16:52.301
Go ahead.

00:16:52.302 --> 00:16:54.221
Well, I'll take your word for it.

00:16:55.014 --> 00:16:57.850
With all this smoke,
we should not stay long.

00:16:58.726 --> 00:17:02.020
Let those who are inside
also go outside immediately.

00:17:02.021 --> 00:17:03.730
I am aware.

00:17:03.731 --> 00:17:07.108
But there may be people
who cannot escape on their own.

00:17:07.109 --> 00:17:09.861
Then we will search for them.

00:17:09.862 --> 00:17:11.363
It is not that simple.

00:17:12.364 --> 00:17:16.160
<i>I really wish the noble one
would stay somewhere safer.</i>

00:17:17.202 --> 00:17:20.872
The daughter of Grand Commandant
is being held here.

00:17:20.873 --> 00:17:23.000
- Here?
- Yes.

00:17:23.584 --> 00:17:27.920
If we abandon her,
a new political enemy will be born, right?

00:17:27.921 --> 00:17:29.965
Indeed.

00:17:33.218 --> 00:17:36.680
Then I will simply do my duty.

00:17:42.811 --> 00:17:43.896
<i>Is that...</i>

00:17:44.980 --> 00:17:48.984
<i>No way. It couldn't be.</i>

00:17:52.613 --> 00:17:55.073
<i>The Forbidden Army will be here soon.</i>

00:17:55.074 --> 00:17:58.744
<i>If I stay, they might think
I am one of the Shi Clan.</i>

00:17:59.536 --> 00:18:00.621
<i>But still.</i>

00:18:01.455 --> 00:18:03.082
I leave the rest to you.

00:18:03.874 --> 00:18:05.917
<i>She should have run.</i>

00:18:05.918 --> 00:18:10.089
<i>What a fool.
But I'm just as bad as Shisui.</i>

00:18:14.343 --> 00:18:17.346
<i>At least let it be someone
who will listen to me!</i>

00:18:34.905 --> 00:18:38.950
Excuse me.
Can you grant me protection, Lord Jinshi?

00:18:38.951 --> 00:18:41.160
Are you injured? You are bleeding.

00:18:41.161 --> 00:18:43.372
No worries, it's not my blood.

00:18:44.039 --> 00:18:45.331
That still counts as a problem!

00:18:45.332 --> 00:18:47.584
- It is snake blood.
- Snake?

00:18:48.669 --> 00:18:51.337
<i>I kind of missed this feeling.</i>

00:18:51.338 --> 00:18:53.924
- Hey, that--
- Huh?

00:18:55.551 --> 00:18:56.844
Crown Prince!

00:18:57.636 --> 00:18:59.720
I am not Crown Prince anymore.

00:18:59.721 --> 00:19:02.515
Consort Gyokuyou has given birth
to the royal heir.

00:19:02.516 --> 00:19:04.059
<i>Crown Prince.</i>

00:19:05.102 --> 00:19:07.854
<i>So that is Lord Jinshi's true identity.</i>

00:19:07.855 --> 00:19:10.231
<i>Things did seem off because
he did not match the supposed age</i>

00:19:10.232 --> 00:19:14.862
<i>of the Emperor's younger brother, 19,
while he himself is 25.</i>

00:19:15.571 --> 00:19:18.031
Lord Jinshi, you look older than your age.

00:19:21.076 --> 00:19:22.995
- Is Lihaku here?
- Yes!

00:19:23.662 --> 00:19:25.080
I'll leave the rest to you.

00:19:30.919 --> 00:19:32.045
Forgive the question,

00:19:33.172 --> 00:19:37.717
but you resemble a Imperial Court girl
named Maomao.

00:19:37.718 --> 00:19:39.051
It's me.

00:19:39.052 --> 00:19:40.803
What are you doing here?

00:19:40.804 --> 00:19:42.014
I was kidnapped.

00:19:42.681 --> 00:19:44.348
Your father.

00:19:44.349 --> 00:19:46.559
Please do not say his name.

00:19:46.560 --> 00:19:48.312
Just say "that old man" or something.

00:19:49.605 --> 00:19:50.647
Got it.

00:19:51.356 --> 00:19:52.316
{\an8}My bad.

00:19:53.066 --> 00:19:55.194
If you say so, I believe it.

00:19:55.777 --> 00:19:59.447
Still, what a mess you are.
Covered in blood.

00:19:59.448 --> 00:20:01.199
It is snake blood.

00:20:01.200 --> 00:20:03.784
Please, don't tell me
you have any injuries.

00:20:03.785 --> 00:20:06.996
That old man pulled his back
trying to do something reckless.

00:20:06.997 --> 00:20:09.498
Now he can't move.

00:20:09.499 --> 00:20:13.085
Was the avalanche and the surprise attack

00:20:13.086 --> 00:20:15.296
part of that old man's plan?

00:20:15.297 --> 00:20:17.090
Yeah.

00:20:18.884 --> 00:20:20.719
Who's sleeping?

00:20:21.303 --> 00:20:24.680
Children. But they're not breathing.

00:20:24.681 --> 00:20:26.433
Seems like they took poison.

00:20:26.934 --> 00:20:28.267
I see.

00:20:28.268 --> 00:20:31.605
Even if they survived,
the entire clan would be executed.

00:20:32.439 --> 00:20:34.107
Women and children alike.

00:20:35.025 --> 00:20:36.360
It is unbearable.

00:20:37.110 --> 00:20:39.111
Will the executed

00:20:39.112 --> 00:20:41.197
be thrown away?

00:20:41.198 --> 00:20:44.617
No, they will be cremated and buried.

00:20:44.618 --> 00:20:48.704
Then, may I at least have them
buried together with their mother?

00:20:48.705 --> 00:20:51.959
That's not my job.

00:20:56.296 --> 00:20:58.548
Looks like they are just sleeping.

00:20:59.258 --> 00:21:01.509
- Hey! Give me a hand here!
- Yes.

00:21:01.510 --> 00:21:03.053
Sir Lihaku?

00:21:04.263 --> 00:21:06.598
We cannot just leave them lying here.

00:21:07.182 --> 00:21:09.558
I cannot grant a proper joint burial,

00:21:09.559 --> 00:21:12.895
but I can quietly bury him
near the cemetery, is what I can do.

00:21:12.896 --> 00:21:14.814
Will you not get in trouble?

00:21:14.815 --> 00:21:18.360
Who knows? If it comes to that,
you figure something out.

00:21:19.278 --> 00:21:21.238
I don't know if I can do
something about it.

00:21:21.863 --> 00:21:24.448
Oh! Got a great idea.

00:21:24.449 --> 00:21:27.743
How about you call that old man "Papa"?

00:21:27.744 --> 00:21:30.037
Then I might do anything.

00:21:30.038 --> 00:21:32.416
Wait, forget I said that!

00:21:38.213 --> 00:21:39.755
That flute?

00:21:39.756 --> 00:21:42.384
A signal. To mark mission complete.

00:21:47.639 --> 00:21:51.810
Now let us go. Getting you out safely

00:21:53.395 --> 00:21:54.771
is my job.

00:22:08.869 --> 00:22:13.040
<i>I will carry out what Shisui
entrusted to me.</i>

00:22:13.540 --> 00:22:14.624
<i>That is all.</i>

00:23:46.091 --> 00:23:49.594
PREVIEW OF THE NEXT EPISODE

00:23:58.061 --> 00:24:00.938
{\an8}<i>The next episode is "The Shi Clan."</i>

00:24:00.939 --> 00:24:01.982
